title: Diamondbacks sweep Rockies as bullpen struggles continue
text:
Published By: Denver Post Rockies - Today 
Thursday night at Chase Field, the Rockies' offense showed life, but their bullpen blew up late in an 8-6 loss to the Arizona Diamondbacks....
